Troll

Table: ForestDragon
Type: Lookup
Roll: 1d100
01-69: Green Dragon
70-86: White Dragon if terrain allows, otherwise Green Dragon
87-90: Black Dragon
90-92: Red Dragon
93-96: Eery Dragon
97-100: Anomalous (Wyrm)

Table: HillDragon
Type: Lookup
Roll: 1d100
01-03: Green Dragon
04-20: White Dragon if terrain allows, otherwise Red Dragon
21-94: Red Dragon
95-96: Eery Dragon
97-100: Anomalous (Wyrm)

Table: MountainDragon
Type: Lookup
Roll: 1d100
01-25: White Dragon if terrain allows, otherwise Red Dragon
26-96: Red Dragon
97-98: Eery Dragon
99-100: Anomalous (Wyrm)

Table: SwampDragon
Type: Lookup
Roll: 1d100
