Type: Lookup
Roll: 1d100
01-85: a Thief
86-96: a Fighter
97-100: an Assassin

Table: MilitaryFactionLeader
Type: Lookup
Roll: 1d100
01-05: a Cleric
06-75: a Fighter
76-95: a Knight
97-100: a Ranger

